line_1: Descend to touch an humbler key,

line_2: 'He fast'ned up the Door with me:

line_1: You fall at once into a lower key,
line_2: That's worse — the drone-pipe of an humble bee.

line_2: Till, as the Sailers in the Haven stay,

line_2: And soon forget the Dangers of the Sea.

line_2: No matter of what kind the subject be.
